  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nWe are launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at Intergalactic Gear.\nWe are creating a “non-guild” guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to Intergalactic Coalition.\nIf you would like to support our efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol\nMetaverse Nomads #121 Star Atlas and Illuvium Drama\nMetaverse Nomads posted a video of their weekly Star Atlas livestream.\nThe Reality of Web3 Gaming | Star Atlas CEO Michael Wagner\nThe Defiant posted a video of an interview with Star Atlas CEO Michael Wagner.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #106\nAephia published their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nSTAR ATLAS #210 FREE MONEY FOR SHIPS, Pyth Airdrop & Star Atlas Update\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video of Star Atlas new updates.\nA Reflection on the 100th Anniversary of The Signature of The Treaty of Peace\nStar Atlas published an article with some lore about Star Atlas.\nNavigating Star Atlas – Limitless Possibilities of Character Customization\nStar Atlas posted a video interview about character customization.\nThe Atlas Brew #89 Polis\nStar Atlas TV posted a video replay of the latest Atlas Brew.\nStar Atlas Recap 11-22-2023\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video recapping the latest Star Atlas news.",
